{"tid":1616149,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路障升級，老鼠膠進場","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T10:07:02.000Z","uid":258748,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55a81b96f36ebcdf769e77367c8c68867f1e3efc","tid":1616149,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:59:55.000Z","msg":"路障係用嚟擋住速龍同防暴推，但係有時又拆得到比車行，咁快拆到既路障又點可靠呢？老鼠膠喺砌實路障同設置陷阱好有用，值得建築師諗諗<br />\n第一，永久模式，將老鼠膠撻喺地面，將路障痴上去，咁就鎖住唔比狗車行同速龍跑過嚟喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二，陷阱模式，用老鼠膠撻喺地面，鋪張唔透氣既膠膜，擺枝唔扭蓋既膠漿喺上面，再用雜物圍住，<span style=\"color: orange;\">咁當狗過嚟拆野時，一粗魯倒瀉成地膠漿，佢地再跑過去，痴晒喺對鞋度，就減速起碼一半喇，仲要成隊嗰日無得再追人添。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">枝膠漿加顏料，仲可以等佢地留下野獸腳印添，水魔法師又可以登場</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38155c94017436504909d4efba74e55e01f7a00","tid":1616149,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08e15d12ae01f7e877cdf8d0818bf00b9e68af0f","tid":1616149,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:03:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bb1783dc576722ddee52f2f41608f11e30f59a9","tid":1616149,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7509a017ea3a36d1f9eeb125e78d189227d98cec","tid":1616149,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:04:42.000Z","msg":"只要係一倒瀉就觸發既陷阱都用得<br />\n趁狗一扯路障就可觸發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f9ae5d19c001e934962c89e8baa855f50a32f1","tid":1616149,"uid":258748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e15d12ae01f7e877cdf8d0818bf00b9e68af0f","tid":1616149,"uid":170445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a81b96f36ebcdf769e77367c8c68867f1e3e